  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Master of Science in Information Systems"
      subtitle="December 2025 at Stevens Institute of Technology, School of Business, Hoboken, NJ"
    >
      GPA: 3.92/4.0<br/>
      Relevant Courses: Data Analytics & Machine Learning, Integrating Information Systems, Data Management, Management of AI
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor of Technology in Electronics Engineering"
      subtitle="May 2020 at St Josephs College of Engineering and Technology, Palai, India"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Research Analyst"
      subtitle="June 2025 – December 2025 at Bachaidus LLC, Bethesda, MD"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-3">
        <li>ML Data Engineering: Performed data preprocessing on financial datasets using Python and Pandas, ensuring high-quality training data for ML models through feature engineering and outlier detection.</li>
        <li>System Architecture: Designed technical architecture for AI-powered platform, identifying scalability improvements for model deployment and real-time inference.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Graduate Teaching Assistant"
      subtitle="September 2025 – December 2025 at Stevens Institute of Technology, Hoboken, NJ"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-3">
        <li>AI Course Instruction: Graded assignments and provided technical feedback for graduate-level Management of AI course, evaluating student understanding of AI ethics, governance, ML deployment strategies, and enterprise AI implementation.</li>
        <li>Student Mentorship: Mentored students on AI project development, prompt engineering techniques, and practical applications of LLMs in business contexts.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Software Developer"
      subtitle="March 2022 – January 2024 at Entym Inc, Delhi, India"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-3">
        <li>ML Data Pipeline: Engineered distributed pipeline using Redis Streams processing 10K+ daily records for ML workflows, improving scalability by 200%.</li>
        <li>Analytics Platform: Built analytics dashboard with 25+ visualizations using SQL, enabling data-driven decisions.</li>
        <li>Full-Stack Development: Developed Vue.js application with intelligent workflow automation and AI-powered recommendation features.</li>
        <li>Cloud Deployment: Deployed containerized applications using Docker on Linux with 99.9% uptime, implementing CI/CD pipelines.</li>
        <li>API Integration: Integrated third-party APIs (payments, communications) establishing foundation for AI service expansion.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Software Engineer"
      subtitle="March 2021 – February 2022 at Claysys Technologies, Kochi, India"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-3">
        <li>NLP Search Platform: Built backend APIs for NLP-based knowledge base with semantic search, reducing retrieval time from minutes to under 5 seconds for 350K+ members.</li>
        <li>Data Aggregation: Developed data aggregation module integrating Finicity and Plaid APIs, enabling instant account linking across 12,000+ financial institutions.</li>
        <li>Team Leadership: Led 3-person API team integrating banking systems, delivering critical financial solutions.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Projects</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Agentic AI Chatbot with LangChain"
      subtitle="September 2025 – October 2025 | LangChain, ReactJS, Python"
    >
      Built an agent system with dynamic tool selection and multi-step reasoning using ReAct pattern. Integrated web search APIs, custom function calling, and real-time streaming.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="RAG Pipeline for Financial Analysis"
      subtitle="June 2025 | RAG, ChromaDB, LangChain"
    >
      Designed end-to-end RAG system integrating LLMs with vector database for context-aware analysis. Implemented document chunking, semantic embeddings, and hybrid search strategies, reducing analysis time by 75%.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Predicting Inflation using Machine Learning"
      subtitle="November 2024 – December 2024 | TensorFlow, Keras"
    >
      Built CNN regression model using TensorFlow to forecast U.S. inflation with 98% accuracy through hyperparameter tuning and feature engineering.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

